title: A Coach
medium: Pen and brown ink on layed paper
description: Sketch of a Carosse.  At left is the front of coach with a small wheel.  Above it sits a coachman's seat with a cushion, hammer cloth, with a scalloped edge, tassels, and fringe.  At center is an oblong shaped body of the coach with a large center window and smaller ones on either side.
name: Drawing
